<i>♪ Only words bleed ♪</i>

1808
01:30:25.342 --> 01:30:29.805
<i>♪ Inside these pages.</i>
<i>you just hold me ♪</i>

1809
01:30:29.930 --> 01:30:32.933
<i>♪ And I won't ever let you go ♪</i>

1810
01:30:33.810 --> 01:30:35.310
<i>♪ You go ♪</i>

1811
